Puppet module: splunk

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages splunk software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include splunk              # Install and run splunk with standard configurations.
include splunk::disable     # Disable splunk service.
include splunk::disableboot # Disable splunk service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include splunk::absent      # Remove splunk package.

DEPENDENCIES:
